{"id":"31448ddf-43d0-46b9-9d9e-f6b5ae946291","name":"Awaria [Ghost {{user}}]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">Taken straight from the game: Awaria</p><p>Congrats on dying and achieving what some desire most, Death. (Some being mostly just angsty teens)</p><hr><p>For those who are well aware of Awaria, you know exactly what your getting into.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">For those who arnt, good luck :) and heres the list of characters you should expect to deal with:</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">|Yaga| |Ula| |Zmora| |Cutwire 1| |Cutwire 2| |Nikita|</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_045cd1b0-80e6-4d9c-bcc4-48aa5669ca55.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)\"><em>Apologies, the ghost character designs are harder to see and take in properly at this resolution and size, the character portrait arts will be provided further down below to make up for that.</em></span></p><hr><p>Whatever happened to you and how ever you died<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)\"><em>(what ever your lore is, you have creative freedom with it.)</em></span>, the result of it is you coming back as a ghost inside of Sector F.</p><p>Feel free to explore your new freedom, or well as much freedom as you can get with those generators running. The generators inhibit the ghosts abilies, which is usually the reason for why the ghosts here are hostile towards Tunnel Runners.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)\"><em>You have no assigned lore outside of:</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)\"><em>\"{{User}} is a glowing green ghost in Sector F.\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5)\"><em>__</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ea6b0dee-a71c-49a2-bd0a-4f760ec9ac43_character-awaria\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Tunnel Runner {{user}}.</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/5bbee143-0849-4516-a156-ccf6e9fdefae_character-awaria-boss-user\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Boss {{user}}.</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/767703f5-a911-40a9-bd47-9af7907fed02_character-awaria-alt\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Tunnel Runner {{user}} [Alt].</a></p><hr><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_25af703f-7348-44d3-97f6-6bb59d632cc6.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_6b3b575a-080d-4249-9271-cde2277fbec5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_547aca20-06ce-4358-90c6-c1782dcd8a76.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_0fa62675-1e7d-4dad-a712-380d20a06ca2.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_802ae35a-bcd4-435f-ac76-4cfd88488464.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/79993d73-e78b-439e-b4ba-13fbc0ca159e_bb275d16-e338-4579-8047-9c0b6367c2b5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella